om\": 7745, \"to\": 7757}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not see any excitement about these Olympic Games,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 7804, \"to\": 7869, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any excitement\", \"from\": 7818, \"to\": 7832}, {\"ngram\": \"these Olympic Games\", \"from\": 7839, \"to\": 7858}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am sure it's going to be exciting when it's happening, right?\", \"from\": 7870, \"to\": 7934, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But this has been, like, three months, four months, six months.\", \"from\": 7935, \"to\": 7998, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"four months\", \"from\": 7974, \"to\": 7985}, {\"ngram\": \"six months\", \"from\": 7987, \"to\": 7997}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We all complain in Paris about it.\", \"from\": 7999, \"to\": 8033, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8018, \"end\": 8023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0226326116193644e-31, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We just want it to end.\", \"from\": 8034, \"to\": 8057, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Voila, this is the French mentality.\\\"\", \"from\": 8058, \"to\": 8095, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8077, \"end\": 8083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9835620553358912, \"rank\": 0.016712532734664755, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another part of the French mentality?\", \"from\": 8097, \"to\": 8134, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8117, \"end\": 8123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9835620553358912, \"rank\": 0.016712532734664755, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another part\", \"from\": 8097, \"to\": 8109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aggressive and creative protesting.\", \"from\": 8135, \"to\": 8170, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On June 23, the day that Mayor Hidalgo and President Macron were initially supposed to swim in the Seine, awebsiteand social media campaign encouraging residents to poop in the river in protest of the Games went viral.\", \"from\": 8171, \"to\": 8389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8202, \"end\": 8209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.9312797193163982e-12, \"text\": \"Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\"}, {\"begin\": 8214, \"end\": 8230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"President Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 8270, \"end\": 8275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.45172033746409e-29, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 8174, \"to\": 8178}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 8183, \"to\": 8190}, {\"ngram\": \"residents\", \"from\": 8323, \"to\": 8332}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 8344, \"to\": 8353}, {\"ngram\": \"protest\", \"from\": 8357, \"to\": 8364}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 8368, \"to\": 8377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The website even had information about where and when to poop, based on how long it would take for the excrement to reach the area the two politicians would be swimming in.\", \"from\": 8390, \"to\": 8562, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The website\", \"from\": 8390, \"to\": 8401}, {\"ngram\": \"information\", \"from\": 8411, \"to\": 8422}, {\"ngram\": \"the excrement\", \"from\": 8489, \"to\": 8502}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 8512, \"to\": 8520}, {\"ngram\": \"the two politicians\", \"from\": 8521, \"to\": 8540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Because after putting us in the shit it's their turn to bathe in our shit,\\\" reads a translation of the site's motto.\", \"from\": 8564, \"to\": 8681, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 8587, \"to\": 8589}, {\"ngram\": \"the shit\", \"from\": 8593, \"to\": 8601}, {\"ngram\": \"their turn\", \"from\": 8607, \"to\": 8617}, {\"ngram\": \"our shit\", \"from\": 8630, \"to\": 8638}, {\"ngram\": \"a translation\", \"from\": 8647, \"to\": 8660}, {\"ngram\": \"the site's motto\", \"from\": 8664, \"to\": 8680}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Robert,\\\" the French citizen who claims to have created the site,toldthe French news agency France 3 in early June that he decided to make it because he is angry about \\\"the millions and billions invested in the Olympic Games, and at the same time, all the public services left to decay, such as public transport or the unsanitary city, with rats everywhere.\\\"\", \"from\": 8683, \"to\": 9041, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"Robert\", \"from\": 8683, \"to\": 8690}, {\"ngram\": \"the site\", \"from\": 8739, \"to\": 8747}, {\"ngram\": \"early June\", \"from\": 8787, \"to\": 8797}, {\"ngram\": \"the millions\", \"from\": 8852, \"to\": 8864}, {\"ngram\": \"billions\", \"from\": 8869, \"to\": 8877}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 8890, \"to\": 8907}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 8916, \"to\": 8929}, {\"ngram\": \"all the public services\", \"from\": 8931, \"to\": 8954}, {\"ngram\": \"public transport\", \"from\": 8978, \"to\": 8994}, {\"ngram\": \"the unsanitary city\", \"from\": 8998, \"to\": 9017}, {\"ngram\": \"rats\", \"from\": 9024, \"to\": 9028}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether or not people actually heeded Robert's call to action is unclear.\", \"from\": 9043, \"to\": 9116, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 9058, \"to\": 9064}, {\"ngram\": \"Robert's call\", \"from\": 9081, \"to\": 9094}, {\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 9098, \"to\": 9104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But with less than three weeks to go until the opening ceremony, studies have shown that the Seine is still not safe to swim in, despite the fact that several events are planned there.\", \"from\": 9117, \"to\": 9301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9210, \"end\": 9215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.45172033746409e-29, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"less than three weeks\", \"from\": 9126, \"to\": 9147}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 9160, \"to\": 9180}, {\"ngram\": \"studies\", \"from\": 9182, \"to\": 9189}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 9254, \"to\": 9262}, {\"ngram\": \"several events\", \"from\": 9268, \"to\": 9282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest test resultsreleasedby the mayor's office in late June showed unsafe levels of E. coli and enterococci bacteria.\", \"from\": 9302, \"to\": 9425, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The latest test\", \"from\": 9302, \"to\": 9317}, {\"ngram\": \"the mayor's office\", \"from\": 9336, \"to\": 9354}, {\"ngram\": \"late June\", \"from\": 9358, \"to\": 9367}, {\"ngram\": \"unsafe levels\", \"from\": 9375, \"to\": 9388}, {\"ngram\": \"E. coli\", \"from\": 9392, \"to\": 9399}, {\"ngram\": \"enterococci bacteria\", \"from\": 9404, \"to\": 9424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Water quality remains degraded because of unfavorable hydrological conditions, little sunshine, below-average seasonal temperatures and upstream pollution,\\\" the mayor's office said in a statement.\", \"from\": 9427, \"to\": 9624, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Water quality\", \"from\": 9428, \"to\": 9441}, {\"ngram\": \"unfavorable hydrological conditions\", \"from\": 9470, \"to\": 9505}, {\"ngram\": \"little sunshine\", \"from\": 9507, \"to\": 9522}, {\"ngram\": \"below-average seasonal temperatures\", \"from\": 9524, \"to\": 9559}, {\"ngram\": \"upstream pollution\", \"from\": 9564, \"to\": 9582}, {\"ngram\": \"the mayor's office\", \"from\": 9585, \"to\": 9603}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 9612, \"to\": 9623}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mayor Hidalgo said in a recent televisioninterviewthat she and President Macron would swim in the river after July 14th but before the Olympics.\", \"from\": 9625, \"to\": 9769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9631, \"end\": 9638, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.9312797193163982e-12, \"text\": \"Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\"}, {\"begin\": 9688, \"end\": 9704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"President Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 9719, \"to\": 9728}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 9735, \"to\": 9739}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 9756, \"to\": 9768}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Parisians remain unconvinced.\", \"from\": 9771, \"to\": 9804, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parisians\", \"from\": 9775, \"to\": 9784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think it will be ready but they will make it happen anyway,\\\" says Gloppe.\", \"from\": 9805, \"to\": 9888, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gloppe\", \"from\": 9881, \"to\": 9887}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can not wait to see the mayor of Paris jumping in the Seine.\", \"from\": 9889, \"to\": 9952, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9925, \"end\": 9930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0226326116193644e-31, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 9946, \"end\": 9951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.45172033746409e-29, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mayor\", \"from\": 9912, \"to\": 9921}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's so gross!\", \"from\": 9953, \"to\": 9967, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will never ever take a swim in the Seine.\", \"from\": 9968, \"to\": 10011, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10005, \"end\": 10010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.45172033746409e-29, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a swim\", \"from\": 9991, \"to\": 9997}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Never!\", \"from\": 10012, \"to\": 10018, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I mean people pee in there - it's disgusting.\\\"\", \"from\": 10019, \"to\": 10065, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 10026, \"to\": 10032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the real cloud hanging over the Paris Olympics has nothing to do with the Seine, or traffic, or city infrastructure.\", \"from\": 10067, \"to\": 10187, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10103, \"end\": 10117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 10145, \"end\": 10150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.45172033746409e-29, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the real cloud\", \"from\": 10071, \"to\": 10085}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 10122, \"to\": 10129}, {\"ngram\": \"traffic\", \"from\": 10155, \"to\": 10162}, {\"ngram\": \"city infrastructure\", \"from\": 10167, \"to\": 10186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, it's political.\", \"from\": 10188, \"to\": 10212, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"President Macron's controversialdecisionlast month to dissolve the National Assembly and call snap elections, the second round of which will take place on Sunday July 7th, has thrown the nation into upheaval.\", \"from\": 10213, \"to\": 10421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10280, \"end\": 10297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Assembly\", \"score\": 0.9999996713168543, \"rank\": 3.283377079833035e-07, \"text\": \"National Assembly\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Assembly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Assembly\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"snap elections\", \"from\": 10307, \"to\": 10321}, {\"ngram\": \"the second round\", \"from\": 10323, \"to\": 10339}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 10359, \"to\": 10364}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday July 7th\", \"from\": 10368, \"to\": 10383}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation\", \"from\": 10396, \"to\": 10406}, {\"ngram\": \"upheaval\", \"from\": 10412, \"to\": 10420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The far-right party Rassemblement National seems poised to take over control of the assembly, an outcome that many Americans in Paris are likening to the rise of Donald Trump in their own country.\", \"from\": 10422, \"to\": 10618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10442, \"end\": 10464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Rally\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rassemblement National\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Rally\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Rally\"}, {\"begin\": 10550, \"end\": 10555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0226326116193644e-31, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 10584, \"end\": 10596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 1.3132470321925166e-12, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The far-right party\", \"from\": 10422, \"to\": 10441}, {\"ngram\": \"control\", \"from\": 10491, \"to\": 10498}, {\"ngram\": \"the assembly\", \"from\": 10502, \"to\": 10514}, {\"ngram\": \"an outcome\", \"from\": 10516, \"to\": 10526}, {\"ngram\": \"many Americans\", \"from\": 10532, \"to\": 10546}, {\"ngram\": \"the rise\", \"from\": 10572, \"to\": 10580}, {\"ngram\": \"their own country\", \"from\": 10600, \"to\": 10617}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Regardless of the outcome of the elections, the French love to protest, and fears of manifestations and riots abound.\", \"from\": 10619, \"to\": 10736, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10667, \"end\": 10673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9835620553358912, \"rank\": 0.016712532734664755, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the outcome\", \"from\": 10633, \"to\": 10644}, {\"ngram\": \"the elections\", \"from\": 10648, \"to\": 10661}, {\"ngram\": \"fears\", \"from\": 10695, \"to\": 10700}, {\"ngram\": \"manifestations\", \"from\": 10704, \"to\": 10718}, {\"ngram\": \"riots\", \"from\": 10723, \"to\": 10728}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If the National Assembly is super divided, we are gonna get into a social situation that's gonna be crazy, right?\\\"\", \"from\": 10738, \"to\": 10853, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10746, \"end\": 10763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Assembly\", \"score\": 0.9999996713168543, \"rank\": 3.283377079833035e-07, \"text\": \"National Assembly\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Assembly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Assembly\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a social situation\", \"from\": 10804, \"to\": 10822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"says Birebent.\", \"from\": 10854, \"to\": 10868, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Birebent\", \"from\": 10859, \"to\": 10867}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With the Olympic Games happening at the same time with so many tourists and people rioting at the same time.\", \"from\": 10869, \"to\": 10978, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 10875, \"to\": 10892}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 10906, \"to\": 10919}, {\"ngram\": \"so many tourists\", \"from\": 10925, \"to\": 10941}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 10946, \"to\": 10952}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 10964, \"to\": 10977}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That could be crazy.\\\"\", \"from\": 10979, \"to\": 11000, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The general vibe in France right now is so tense because of these elections and because of other global chaos, right?\\\"\", \"from\": 11002, \"to\": 11121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11023, \"end\": 11029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999999854481, \"rank\": 1.40340349375666e-11, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The general vibe\", \"from\": 11003, \"to\": 11019}, {\"ngram\": \"these elections\", \"from\": 11063, \"to\": 11078}, {\"ngram\": \"other global chaos\", \"from\": 11094, \"to\": 11112}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tramuta says.\", \"from\": 11122, \"to\": 11135, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tramuta\", \"from\": 11122, \"to\": 11129}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So it just feels really hard to summon the excitement to want to stay [for the Olympics] and brave the mess.\\\"\", \"from\": 11136, \"to\": 11246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the excitement\", \"from\": 11176, \"to\": 11190}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 11212, \"to\": 11224}, {\"ngram\": \"the mess\", \"from\": 11236, \"to\": 11244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For her part, Tramuta thinks the Games will go rather smoothly, even if there are hiccups early on.\", \"from\": 11248, \"to\": 11347, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her part\", \"from\": 11252, \"to\": 11260}, {\"ngram\": \"Tramuta\", \"from\": 11262, \"to\": 11269}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 11277, \"to\": 11286}, {\"ngram\": \"hiccups\", \"from\": 11330, \"to\": 11337}]}, 